title: DDFP 458: Best Super Bowl Cities & Top 100 Players
itunes:title: DDFP 458: Best Super Bowl Cities & Top 100 Players
description:
Shek is joined by NFL Media’s Maurice Jones-Drew, Ike Taylor, and Gregg Rosenthal to debate what NFL player could completely change their image by winning a championship. The guys then critique J.J. Watt’s new logo while coming up with symbols of their own. MJD and Rosenthal also settle a score over their own Top-100 rankings.
